         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Langensalza, 27th July, 1889. ¶ Highly esteemed Sir, ¶  ¶ For your esteemed address, I am obliged to Professor Magnus, ¶  Berlin, who also encouraged me to direct a humble inquiry to you. I should lik...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">89.07.27a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Franz Heydrich</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M108b, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Annotated by M: 'Beantw. [Answered] 31/10/89'. Letter not found.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Langensalza, d. 27. Juli 1889.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochgeehrter Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihre werthe Adresse verdanke ich Herrn Professor Magnus Berlin, auch hat mich derselbe ermuthigt eine bescheidene Anfrage an Sie zu richten. Ich möchte später einmal ein Werk über Meeresalgen herausgeben, zu welchem Zweck ich auch in Australiens Meeren sammeln lassen wollte.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Meine bescheidene und höfliche Frage geht nun dahin, ob durch Ihre güte es möglich wäre, Jemand dort ausfindig zu machen, von dem ich käuflich Meeresalgen sammeln lassen könnte, um mir dieselben getrocknet oder als Spiritus-Präparat zuzuschicken. Ich würde gern die höchsten Honorare zahlen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Beifolgend einige Postmarken, zur gütigen Beantwortung; Sie würden mich wenigstens dadurch zu grösstem Dank verpflichten.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit vorzügl. Hochachtung</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. Heydrich</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Meine Adresse ist:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">F. Heydrich</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Langensalza</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Deutschland.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Langensalza, 27th July, 1889.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Highly esteemed Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For your esteemed address, I am obliged to Professor Magnus,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">P. W. Magnus.</p>
               </note> Berlin, who also encouraged me to direct a humble inquiry to you. I should like to publish a work on marine algae at some later date, for which purpose I should also like to have the Australian oceans collected.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My humble and polite query is, whether it would be possible through your kindness to find somebody there, who would collect marine algae for me for payment, and send them to me dried or as spirit preparations. I should be happy to pay the highest fees.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Although Heydrich published accounts of the algae of German New Guinea and some new species from New Zealand (for example, Heydrich (1892) and Heydrich (1893)), and some other regionally focused studies, no publication specifically on Australian marine algae has been found.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed some postage stamps for your kind reply, by which alone you would place me under the greatest obligation.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With greatest respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. Heydrich.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My address is:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">F. Heydrich</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Langensalza</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Germany.</p>
         </div>
